    "biography": "<p>A vast, wise Awakened whale (Megaptera palestrina) whose songs carry memory and meaning; it reincarnates alternately as male and female.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Animal Control (Fish, Aquatic Mammals), Compulsion (Zone ×5), Dismissal (Zone ×5), Empathy (LOS), Engulf, Enhanced Senses (Sonar), Immunity to Normal Weapons, Influence (LOS), Magic Sense, Search, Sonic Projection</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Dietary Requirement (Krill)</p><p><em>Attacks: 15D, Reach +1. Habitat: Cold/cool oceans. Range: Arctic oceans (autumn/winter), North and Baltic seas (spring/summer). 3D6 Initiative dice. Body 20, Strength 14, Essence 9 — whale-scale. Book Body 20/2. PAE p.69.</em></p>",
